bf","tid":2491033,"uid":77625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"300fce8da51233d992b0edbf230684d3201e941d","tid":2491033,"uid":279981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b00221e0861d9024afc5a84aadbb162bd67cd247","tid":2491033,"uid":9542,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T04:50:52.000Z","msg":"呢個論壇、立場蘋果果啲好快執柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T05:00:24.000Z","msg":"咁就可以決心走人囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T05:33:17.000Z","msg":"放心 點差都好 大部分人都唔會走"},{"pid":"8756cd4de30962e748ae679a105dfced973a3466","tid":2491033,"uid":253553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f40d52549ff125c886eff407433490de167e9248","tid":2491033,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T04:45:42.000Z","msg":"警務處處長鄧炳強在立法會財委會特別會議上表示，「假新聞」與國家安全有直接關係，又說昨日已提到，不少外部勢力利用在香港的代理人，用「假新聞」、假消息的方法，在香港煽動仇恨、分化社會、製造矛盾等，而他昨日的言論今日已在報紙一一應驗。鄧炳強說，對於嘗試用假新聞危害香港安全的人，警方會全面調查，一有證據就會作出拘捕及檢控。<br />\n<br />\n鄧炳強提到，警隊在招募上遇到挑戰，包括有人抹黑警隊，打擊警隊威信，投考者亦面對同儕壓力、起底、工作太辛勞等問題。鄧炳強指出，發現有人會刻意抹黑親近警隊的人，他舉例今日有報章頭條，將昨日警隊開放日，在警隊設施中玩得很開心、天真爛漫的一班學生，抹黑成與「黑暴」有關，他批評做法非常不道德，除了傷害小朋友的心，亦反映有人想用恐嚇的方法，抹黑想親近警隊的人。<br />\n<br />\n保安局局長李家超表示，同意要處理「假新聞」的問題，但認為同時「正義」的訊息亦要「走出來」。他指出，現時本港局勢向好發展，但仍潛伏風險，不法份子仍沒有放棄，繼續通過不同手段鼓吹及宣傳港獨，以及破壞行為，包括通過媒體、刊物及文化藝術等，有媒體刻意將罪犯塑造英雄故事，所以社會要共建守法意識，同時要理直氣壯指出問題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1586120-20210416.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1586120-20210416.htm&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLaGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=bf429e9f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1586120-20210416.htm&h=2c702818\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1586120-20210416.htm</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T05:34:14.000Z","msg":"唔同警察frd = 犯國安法"},{"pid":"9ef1bbced74ffd2c743788b85d3a68cbd38f9fb4","tid":2491033,"uid":49574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T05:34:21.000Z","msg":"道具場景同人都係佢地出 請問假在邊度？"},{"pid":"6147b787bd1286d027d351600dae1256499bd6b8","tid":2491033,"uid":56984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T05:35:23.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">你講就真啊<br />\n屌你老母</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"728110e13686374a2365bd3b2ffbf22f7fe0385b","tid":2491033,"uid":21141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T05:35:54.000Z","msg":"香港警察Facebook咪係囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"733596c03974b24408d84b130f555b4ad014cdc6","tid":2491033,"uid":266519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T05:37:06.000Z","msg":"咁tvb大獲囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aa2e89c41f0e85a5f865ee3570daa7c30307585","tid":2491033,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T05:37:07.000Z","msg":"你想捉雜斤平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44fa8d080b43eaa480856ef0945a942919766757","tid":2491033,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T05:37:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bc41758b51bfd9944102529695ccf17a77e416b","tid":2491033,"uid":305358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T05:38:08.000Z","msg":"賊喊捉賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b525ee6a9a8e8ddf8b78fb71ad101daf3a239f6f","tid":2491033,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T05:38:51.000Z","msg":"你自己咪係囉 查麥能"},{"pid":"657fe35925ed964e45