s.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1586120-20210416.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1586120-20210416.htm&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLaGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=bf429e9f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1586120-20210416.htm&h=2c702818\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1586120-20210416.htm</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T06:02:37.000Z","msg":"咩係假新聞？save HK戈啲？"},{"pid":"3fe20ee841e4c19082d66dd2f4d97386fdb85663","tid":2491033,"uid":705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T06:04:48.000Z","msg":"張相唔係新華社影既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a4843721dd6e3aa2f92ea69d7e8e0e7f6194d1d","tid":2491033,"uid":271513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T06:10:09.000Z","msg":"係同堆殘害平民的黑暴警甴有關喎<br />\n<br />\n有講錯咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n班恐怖份子仲成日做假新聞添"},{"pid":"57f187dd1e801f305cd43b72353cee1700152228","tid":2491033,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T06:11:29.000Z","msg":"唔洗煽動，憎恨你一生。無和解，除非你策反。"},{"pid":"ca0e05769f733e0744976af31df266df00b769cc","tid":2491033,"uid":4964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T06:12:18.000Z","msg":"假新聞大國有面話人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dbe5b41d193923b6a61b02aa87f14c7311b5604","tid":2491033,"uid":45910,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6e4cf03a9835cb3c783072cc37b41f86a9402c80","tid":2491033,"uid":210161,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T04:49:09.000Z","msg":"尋日張相，假新聞？<br />\n<br />\n唔需要任何文字 大家都明張相既意思"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T06:13:25.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">今日有報章頭條，將昨日警隊開放日，在警隊設施中玩得很開心、天真爛漫的一班學生，抹黑成與「黑暴」有關</span><br />\n<br />\n我同意係假新聞，佢地應該係